TEXT.S: Dalia Grybauskait ryax sa tay 1 nqu tay 3, Dalia Grybauskait , squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay 1956) mrhuw Lithuania ta' misuw hya' ga Dalia Grybauskait , aring ryax tay 12 squ byacing tay 7 sa kawas 2009 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. sraral hiya yaya Vitalija Korsakait (1922 1989) hintgan maki Bir ai qalang. praw mtbaziy na squilq. hiya yaba Polikarpas Grybauskas (1928 2008) ptzyuwaw ringki ru ppiray turuy pincyogan nya. te sazing cinbwanan mciriq praw NKVD mhetay. Grybauskait Jawas bah Salom ja N ris . cyux sazing mtswe', qutux maki Lithuania, qutux maki Colorado Springs. hiya smoya biru na zywaw kinbkisan,k'kian ru uli. 11 kawas, Grybauskait aring sangka' unro. squilq na unro. 19 kawas, hiya qutux kawas pinyuwagan la, galan pkensa pincyogan nya, maki Lithuanian koka Philharmonic . Grybauskait mqwas beh Saint Petersburg State krahu' pqwasan. trang son Leningrad A.A.sezi' ggalan pila na seto. t'aring mtzyaw koba maki Saint Petersburg. 1983 kawas, spiyang magal zyaw na sakinning maki Vilnius. 1983 1989 kawas 12 byacing, hiya ga Communist Party. 1989 kawas 12 byacing lahan CPSU, CPL squilq, tehoq 1990 kawas 6 byacing. qnxan nya Grybauskait ungat laqi ru ini kekong. hiya baq cingay ke' ego, Russian ,Polish ru baq kmal Frenc .
